    <lb n="2"/>τιμιωτάτωι χαί<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρε</supplied>ιν. 

    <lb n="3"/>πάνυ ἥσθην <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἀ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">κού</supplied>ων σε ἐν τῷ Θεινίτῃ 

    <lb n="4"/>διάγειν καὶ συνήδομαί γε <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied>ῷ φίλῳ 

    <lb n="5"/>σο<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">υ</supplied> κηδεμόνι ἀγαθῷ καὶ <choice><corr>ἐπι<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ει</supplied>κε-

